NUMBER 569
NAME Forester's Guild
FOREST
DAY_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
Trees of all varieties, shapes and sizes, grow thickly on either side
of the path, yet the trees do not have an ominous, suffocating appearance,
rather they fill you with peace and serenity. In the middle of the path
sits a boulder with a gold plaque mounted on it. The path leads back out
of the copse. A leafy arch leads to the heart of the Forester's Grove.
To the northeast, you see the pride of the area, the majestic Silver Oak.
*DESCRIPTION_END
