NUMBER 572
NAME Forester's Guild, Shop
INDOOR_GROUND
DAY_LIGHT
FLETCHER
*DESCRIPTION_START
Nestled in this shack is the workshop of Qounvar Martham and his apprentices.
They painstakingly labor over the finest yew bows and arrows in all of Fayd,
which are sold only to members of the Forester Guild. Besides the yew bows, the
distinctive tunics worn by Forester members are sold here. A small sign lists
the items and prices. To one side of the room, tools have been set aside for
Foresters who like to make their own weapons.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT O 2268
;------------sign--------------
ITEM 0 204 ADJ1=355
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM READ 0
	ITEM                    PRICE
	----                    -----
	Yew bow               500 Crowns
	Arrows                  3 Shillings
	Forester tunic          5 Crowns
	Mistletoe               3 Crowns

      Notice: reselling forester items to
      nonmembers is grounds for dismissal.

      Please just say the name of the item
      you wish to purchase.
      
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFSAY bow
	IFVAR WEALTH < 50000
        	ECHO PLAYER Qounvar informs you that you do not have enough money to buy a bow.
   	ELSE
   		IFITEM 8
   			ECHO PLAYER Qounvar says, "Sorry, you need to get the other item first so there is room."
        	ELSE
        		SUB WEALTH 50000
  			NEWITEM 8 8 ADJ1=25 ADJ2=400 VAL2=40
  			ECHO PLAYER Qounvar sets a black yew bow in front of you. "This is a sweet one, you know? It will serve you well."
  			ECHO OTHERS Qounvar places a black yew bow in front of %N.
		ENDIF
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB GET -1
	IFVAR ARCHNUM = 8
		IFVAR ITEMBIT6 = 0
			EQUAL ITEMBIT6 1
			EQUAL ITEMBIT14 1
		ENDIF
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY arrows
	IFVAR WEALTH < 30
        	ECHO PLAYER Qounvar informs you that you do not have enough money to buy any arrows.
   	ELSE
   		IFITEM 8
   			ECHO PLAYER Qounvar says, "Sorry, you need to get the other item first so there is room."
        	ELSE   	
        		SUB WEALTH 30
  			NEWITEM 8 1804 ADJ1=399
  			ECHO PLAYER Qounvar sets a bundle of forester arrows in front of you. "Just made these today."
  			ECHO OTHERS Qounvar places a bundle of arrows in front of %N.
  		ENDIF
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY tunic
	IFVAR WEALTH < 500
        	ECHO PLAYER Qounvar informs you that you do not have enough money to buy a tunic.
   	ELSE
   		IFITEM 8
   			ECHO PLAYER Qounvar says, "Sorry, you need to get the other item first so there is room."
        	ELSE   	
        		SUB WEALTH 500
  			NEWITEM 8 285 ADJ1=399
  			ECHO PLAYER Qounvar sets a fresh new tunic in front of you. "Wear it proudly."
  			ECHO OTHERS Qounvar places a fresh new tunic in front of %N.
		ENDIF
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY Mistletoe
	IFVAR WEALTH < 300
        	ECHO PLAYER Qounvar informs you that you do not have enough money to buy any mistletoe.
   	ELSE
   		IFITEM 8
   			ECHO PLAYER Qounvar says, "Sorry, you need to get the other item first so there is room."
        	ELSE   	
        		SUB WEALTH 300
  			NEWITEM 8 1500
  			ECHO PLAYER Qounvar sets a sprig of mistletoe in front of you.
  			ECHO OTHERS Qounvar places a sprig of mistletoe in front of %N.
		ENDIF
	ENDIF
ENDIF
